Package: GenScreenBayes
Title: Tweedie-Based Empirical Bayes Genomic Screening
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Himel", "Mallick",
           email = "you@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("A. Lawrence", "Gould",
           email = "larry_gould@merck.com",
           role = "aut")
  )
Description: Tools for empirical Bayes genomic screening using Tweedie mixture
    models. Provides functions to estimate control and test Tweedie parameters,
    compute marginal densities and likelihood ratios, evaluate survival
    probabilities for test-control differences, perform posterior inference
    for pi0, and obtain gene-level screening probabilities, with plotting
    utilities for posterior pi0 summaries.
